---
/**
 * Quote — case-page user quote, styled as a `.dc-quote` blockquote
 * (italic, accent-color quote mark, slightly inset). Used for verbatim
 * user research excerpts.
 *
 * Usage in MDX:
 *   <Quote>«Can I get a better settlement? I thought each one saved 50%.»</Quote>
 */
---
<blockquote class="dc-quote">
  <slot />
</blockquote>
